          <scopecontent>
            <p>The panel titled Surveillance &amp; Dataveillance consisted of three speakers:</p>
            <p>
              <list type="simple">
                <item>Lapity, Jon -- (part 1)</item>
                <item>Corsetti, George -- (part 1) ("He documents specifics of police surveillance and infiltration of various Mich. area groups. The maintaining of files, informers and dirty tricks.")</item>
                <item>Morgan, Chuck, ACLU -- <title render="italic">Electronic Surveillance Systems and Computer Data</title> (p 2) ("A speech everyone should hear. He outlines the use of satellites, computers, voiceprints, wire-tapping. The CIA, Dept. of Defense, the NSA. An Orwellian nightmare. Very good question and answer period follows.")</item>
